import requests

url = "https://startup-funding.p.rapidapi.com/api-july22-v1-fund-all"

    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "startup-funding.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
